                <img class="img-fluid shadow-lg rounded-3" src="~/images/WhoAreWe.png" alt="Who We Are" style="max-width: 70%; height: auto;">
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>
    <!-- Who We Are Section end -->
    <section class="section bg-dark-3">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center p-5 gap-5">
            <div class="col-lg-5 my-auto text-center">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-lg" src="~/images/CorePrinciples.png" alt="Our Mission" style="max-width: 70%; height: auto;">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex order-1 order-lg-2">
                <div class="my-auto px-0 px-lg-5">
                    <!-- Core Principles Section -->
                    <h4 class="text-5 fw-500 text-primary">Core Principles</h4>
                    <p class="text-3">
                        Your digital assets are in safe hands with us. We implement top-tier encryption techniques and cutting-edge security protocols to keep your data secure at all times.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-3">
                        We don’t just keep up with the times; we set the pace. Our relentless focus on innovation ensures that our platform remains at the forefront of technology, providing you with a superior user experience.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-3">
                        You are the reason we exist. Every feature we develop is guided by your feedback and designed to meet your unique needs. We listen, we learn, and we deliver.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Our Purpose Section -->
                    <h4 class="text-5 fw-500 text-primary mt-5">Our Purpose</h4>
                    <p class="text-3">
                        Imagine a world where managing your digital assets is as simple as a few clicks. That’s our mission—to transform your financial experience with a platform that’s secure, intuitive, and accessible to everyone, putting you in full control of your digital journey.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Our Aspiration Section -->
                    <h4 class="text-5 fw-500 text-primary mt-5 mb-2">Our Aspiration</h4>
                    <p class="text-3">
                        We’re not just another virtual wallet. We aspire to be your trusted partner in the digital finance world, offering a solution that’s reliable, innovative, and always transparent.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Our Ambition Section -->
                    <h4 class="text-5 fw-500 text-primary mt-5 mb-2">Our Ambition</h4>
                    <p class="text-3">
                        Our goal is nothing short of excellence. We aim to become the global leader in virtual wallet services, continuously pushing the boundaries of what’s possible in financial technology.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Our Values and Mission Section end -->


